I"◊<p><a href="/assets/Knob/done.jpg"><img src="/assets/Knob/Thumbnails/done.jpg" alt="All done!" /></a></p>

<p>I have a <a href="https://us.focusrite.com/firewire-audio-interfaces/saffire-pro-40">Focusrite Saffire Pro 40</a> that is setup as part of my live rig. To change the master volume, it requires that I reach down and blindly grab the correct one of about 30 knobs. If you haven‚Äôt guessed, I rarely get it.</p>

<p>The solution is simple. Make a bigger knob out of sapele, of course.</p>

<!--more-->

<h1 class="no_toc" id="contents">Contents</h1>
<ul id="markdown-toc">
