  <li><a href="#give-it-the-d-part-1" id="markdown-toc-give-it-the-d-part-1">Give it the D, part 1</a></li>
  <li><a href="#give-it-the-d-part-2" id="markdown-toc-give-it-the-d-part-2">Give it the D, part 2</a></li>
  <li><a href="#some-indication" id="markdown-toc-some-indication">Some Indication</a></li>
